00:19:27.720 --> 00:19:28.520
Keluarga?

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:29.800
Keluarga apa?

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:31.720
Kalian iri dengan
kesuksesan satu sama lain!

00:19:31.760 --> 00:19:34.840
Dimpy, jika kamu
sangat menentang

00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:36.040
